verbose_text: Compared with the cells that were transfected with Ha-labeled-USP4 or Myc-labeled-IRF4 alone, when Ha-USP4 and Myc-IRF4 were coexpressed, immunoprecipitation of Ha-USP4 using anti-Ha antibody resulted in the co-immunoprecipitation of Myc-IRF4 as detected by immunoblotting with anti-Myc antibodies.
